weird/&quot; title=&quot;people sometimes ask me what I&amp;#039;m working on, well here are a few things that I haven&amp;#039;t invested any time in at all, but find odd. Check them out at your own peril.&quot;&gt;Vulnerability Lab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ha.ckers.org/charsets.html&quot; title=&quot;Chart of charsets with various vulnerabilities&quot;&gt;Vulnerable Charsets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ha.ckers.org/webbug.html&quot; title=&quot;Another interesting way to include a webbug in .doc files&quot;&gt;webbug in .doc files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://ha.ckers.org/xss.html&quot; title=&quot;XSS cheatsheet - Esp: for filter evasion&quot;&gt;XSS Cheat Sheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
